reviewText: These are for the wife who constantly reminds men that it reminds her of us 30+ years and 3 Children ago, I have purchased all of the available Be Careful With My heart DVD's and since they are now slow in releasing new ones my wife has started to watch them over and over again. She has vol. 1- 31 and the fairytale wedding and druling at the mouth for more. Hurry Please She has started her 3rd trip thru the dvd's
